H & R Block , Compuserve make appointments . H & R Block Inc said Monday it has named Frank Salizzoni president and chief executive . Its subsidiary , CompuServe Corp , also announced it has named Salizzoni chairman of the board . At CompuServe , Salizzoni replaces Henry Frigon , who served in the chairman ' s position on an interim basis . He will remain on the board , and Bob Massey continues as CompuServe ' s president and chief executive . At H & R Block , Salizzoni has been president and chief executive on an interim basis since June 19 . 
